yo" title="Tenrikyo">Tenrikyo</a> <span typeof="mw:File"><a href="/wiki/File:Tenrikyo_emblem.svg" class="mw-file-description"><img src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Tenrikyo_emblem.svg/18px-Tenrikyo_emblem.svg.png" decoding="async" width="18" height="18" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Tenrikyo_emblem.svg/27px-Tenrikyo_emblem.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/f7/Tenrikyo_emblem.svg/36px-Tenrikyo_emblem.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="680" data-file-height="680" /></a></span></div></th></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style="background:#DDA0DD;width:1%">People</th><td class="navbox-list-with-group navbox-list navbox-odd hlist" style="width:100%;padding:0"><div style="padding:0 0.25em">
